+           MAC.L       @r3+,@r4+
+           MAC.L       @r3+,@r4+
+   	  STS	      mach,r1
+ 	  STS	      macl,r0
+ 	  XTRCT	      r1,r0      ! r0 = M01*cos+M02*sin
