+ !----------------------------------------------------------------------------
+ !  mth_norm.src -- MTH ���C�u���� �@���x�N�^�v�Z ���W���[��
+ !  Copyright(c) 1994 SEGA
+ !  Written by H.E on 1994-06-22 Ver.1.00
